      <title>特朗普第二次攻击全球气候秩序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-01-30/the-global-climate-order-teeters-under-second-assault-by-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普第二次退出《巴黎协定》，对气候行动来说，这是一个更加动荡的时期，民粹主义的兴起和企业的撤退给美国撤退增加了更大的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-01-30/the-global-climate-order-teeters-under-second-assault-by-trump</guid>
